{"tid":2493081,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"幻愛、狂舞派3、一秒拳王，你會點排？","createTime":"2021-04-17T15:06:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T18:38:58.000Z","uid":87511,"like":13,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"805c2af0f83910666ff32954f44c6290c34ea335","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:06:54.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意係狂舞派3，之後係一秒拳王，最後係幻愛<br />\n<br />\n幻愛：<br />\n劇情一般<br />\n痴線佬遇著閪痕港女<br />\n睇唔出有咩大道理想講<br />\n唯一印象最深刻係欣欣對男主角講嘅一句對白：<br />\n「雖然我嘅存在係假，但係我哋之間嘅感情係真」（意思大致係咁）<br />\n我覺得呢句喺套戲入面嘅地位就等於一秒拳王入面嗰句「<del>柒咗</del>避唔到，一齊捱」<br />\n<br />\n狂舞派3：<br />\n我本身唔識hip hop<br />\n但係除咗感受到一班演員對hip hop嘅熱愛<br />\n成套戲其實都係圍繞緊香港嘅選舉<br />\n姑勿論你同唔同意佢嘅立場都好, 我都睇到好有共鳴<br />\n同埋有時聽佢首歌會聽到眼濕濕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n《歡迎嚟到呢座城市》<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwrRmAuWzQw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgwrRmAuWzQw&d=suC3bgMk4yzoLj7oQdk4RA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ee66101e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gwrRmAuWzQw</a><br />\n<br />\n一秒拳王：<br />\n身邊好多人睇完再睇<br />\n少有會睇到眼濕濕嘅一套戲<br />\n特別係國腎個仔瞓醫院病房兩仔爺一齊傾計嗰幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇嘢想補充<br />\n<br />\nBtw我仲未睇金都、夜香鴛鴦深水埗，好羞愧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a8014fdfe4ffc46afe04226bf056cac30a0176","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，開post唔夠一分鐘就兩個腐皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db877fe4a9238d5836b4cc979a694463511fe4f9","tid":2493081,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a8014fdfe4ffc46afe04226bf056cac30a0176","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，開post唔夠一分鐘就兩個腐皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"喺連登屌幻愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab290eb75f1f93f15b8defc22e8dae13280e2d8","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"db877fe4a9238d5836b4cc979a694463511fe4f9","tid":2493081,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a8014fdfe4ffc46afe04226bf056cac30a0176","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:08:00.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，開post唔夠一分鐘就兩個腐皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:16:53.000Z","msg":"喺連登屌幻愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"討論下, 冇傷肝<br />\n大家都鍾意高質港產戲"},{"pid":"e026743204e5b8a5c438c3889fa903e61d30e5c4","tid":2493081,"uid":40862,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"一定係幻愛。太真"},{"pid":"a53e892b3800360677ce7d7b0b535ec39eb679d7","tid":2493081,"uid":186600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:29:51.000Z","msg":"一秒拳王"},{"pid":"530a9ea460805738b625efff4107bcb7b69b353a","tid":2493081,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"一套葉問4已經屌打曬呢啲低成本新導演無聊傷春悲秋片啦<br />\n我仲睇咗兩次添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eeacdd8ad7d3a4ca2878937dc7e8b161b6c93b9","tid":2493081,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530a9ea460805738b625efff4107bcb7b69b353a","tid":2493081,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"一套葉問4已經屌打曬呢啲低成本新導演無聊傷春悲秋片啦<br />\n我仲睇咗兩次添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走啦你, 我唔想搞大佢"},{"pid":"721cc1f0ace653abba1f7339aea8f0f6f8b1ead1","tid":2493081,"uid":53612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:05:19.000Z","msg":"一<br />\n幻<br />\n狂"},{"pid":"333ab72b825d885bc4b69ea8d7b85bd3a86e8435","tid":2493081,"uid":320253,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"一秒拳王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166c93d14770468752f5d81f73dcb92bde0a237a","tid":2493081,"uid":71393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:15:51.000Z","msg":"睇哂金都叔叔幻愛夜香鴛鴦深水埗一秒拳王<br />\n反而無睇狂舞派3<br />\n個人咁排<br />\n一秒拳王&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;金都&gt;&gt;&gt;叔叔&gt;&gt;幻愛&gt;夜香鴛鴦深水埗"},{"pid":"812af92812d4d5893dbc59cac8d4833df2ce8b8f","tid":2493081,"uid":381291,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:22:50.000Z","msg":"一秒拳王＞幻愛＞狂舞派3<br />\n<br />\n以下個人觀點 唔好屌咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n狂舞派3拖戲拖到好冗長，太多支線故事交代得好唔清楚，例如佳仔、係咁loop好人一生平安個呀婆嗰啲，同埋最後個結尾完得好突然，好似高潮到一半就冇貨咁。<br />\n<br />\n幻愛唔知點解，我個人覺得有啲悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能戀愛題材唔係個個啱，但係係好特別嘅戀愛題材，係我自己冇乜feel姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一秒拳王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我前前後後睇咗3次，第一次睇完覺得好熱血，喊到收唔到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一個喊位係良仔醫院嗰幕，比個豆釘搞到笑中有淚，個父子情真係又催淚又搞笑（btw 良仔勁得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）第二個係天仁喺另一個平行時空爬翻起身嗰幕，好唔識形容呢種感覺，因為套戲有好多對白同橋段我都覺得係對香港人嘅暗示，所以呢幕我自己聯想咗好多嘢，然後爆喊，然後同自己講一定要睇第二次第三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d1df76d8c4616ad36b189bfe01d86f84eee29e4","tid":2493081,"uid":154017,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:49:47.000Z","msg":"狂舞派3&gt;幻愛=一秒拳王"},{"pid":"1e6f79523dfcccbe8015c3b43e65281a734c7289","tid":2493081,"uid":23672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:55:15.000Z","msg":"三套都正野"},{"pid":"784279fe661b0526ffadb5520d144c555bf1a83c","tid":2493081,"uid":184756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"530a9ea460805738b625efff4107bcb7b69b353a","tid":2493081,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T15:37:29.000Z","msg":"一套葉問4已經屌打曬呢啲低成本新導演無聊傷春悲秋片啦<br />\n我仲睇咗兩次添<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T16:56:46.000Z","msg":"鍾意食屎重要周圍同人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d501d9f3839091505841e324e816617dd7fe25b","tid":2493081,"uid":279463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:00:12.000Z","msg":"狂舞派3 &gt;= 一秒拳王 = 幻愛<br />\n真係好難排"},{"pid":"715e8655bf04215be0a25de1798867a7742846f2","tid":2493081,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"幻愛＞一秒拳王＞狂舞派3"},{"pid":"bf49707c8424fa65a53e48887b12bc14e25d8d26","tid":2493081,"uid":157304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"715e8655bf04215be0a25de1798867a7742846f2","tid":2493081,"uid":30510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T17:01:05.000Z","msg":"幻愛＞一秒拳王＞狂舞派3"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T18:22:04.000Z","msg":"Same"},{"pid":"539ab21ffba6c6e3ee1f75baf5eee1606dbf75a4","tid":2493081,"uid":372441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"其實幻愛唔係愛情電影"},{"pid":"a71c3f1000f7625989a3262f5ecba76be6d031d8","tid":2493081,"uid":359589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T18:38:08.000Z","msg":"一秒＞狂＞幻愛"},{"pid":"dd5cdc4b8c595b1bfa702652f46eb7bf4c031d36","tid":2493081,"uid":120660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"一秒拳王&gt;幻愛&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;狂舞派3"}]}